<!-- how it works section  -->
<section id="how-it-works">
	<div class="container holder">
	  <div class="row">
	    <div class="col-lg-6 col-md-6 col-sm-6 col-xs-12 box">
        <h2>We Power On-Demand Storage</h2>
        <p>We pioneered the On-Demand Storage industry in New York City and San Francisco. We now run a software platform that powers On-Demand Storage services delivered by anyone.</p>
	    </div>

	    <div class="col-lg-6 col-md-6 col-sm-6 col-xs-12 box">
				<div class="form-holder">
					<div class="panel panel-default">
						<div class="panel-body centered-title">
							<h4>Find On-Demand Storage in your city.</h4>

							<small><%= link_to "Add your service", new_company_path %></small><br/>
								<small>
									Boxbee is the leading provider of on demand storage software. See companies that offer storage, pickup, and delivery services.
								</small>
								<div class="centered-button">
									<%= link_to "View on demand companies", companies_path, class: 'btn-login' %>
								</div>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
      </div>
	  </div>

	  <div class="row">
	    <div class="col-sm-6 col-xs-12 col-sm-push-6 box">

          <p>If you provide On-Demand Storage services to your customers (or want to) and are interested in early access to our On-Demand Storage platform, join the Boxbee Beta program.</p>
          <p><%= link_to "Apply to the Boxbee Beta program", beta_program_path %></p>
	    </div>

      <div class="col-sm-6 col-xs-12 col-sm-pull-6 box">
        <div class="img-holder">
          <%= image_tag 'Boxbee-02.svg', alt: "Boxbee" %>
        </div>
      </div>
	  </div>

	  <div class="row">
	    <div class=" col-md-6 col-sm-6 col-xs-12 box">

        <p>We're always on the lookout for daring, smart, nice people who are interested in doing big things. Join our growing team.</p>

	    </div>

	    <div class=" col-md-6 col-sm-6 col-xs-12 box">
	      <div class="img-holder">
					<div class="panel panel-default">
						<div class="panel-body">
							<h2 id="job-openings">Job openings</h2>
							<div id="whr_embed_hook"></div>
						</div>
					</div>
	      </div>
      </div>
	  </div>
	</div>
</section>

<script src='https://www.workable.com/assets/embed.js' type='text/javascript'></script>
<script type='text/javascript' charset='utf-8'>
	$(document).ready('read page:load', function(){
	whr_embed(8394, {detail: 'titles', base: 'jobs', zoom: 'city', grouping: 'none'});
	});
</script>
